data.name: HighlightMovieDescription
data.value: Based on the true story of Jordan Belfort, from his rise to a wealthy stock-broker living the high life to his fall involving crime, corruption and the federal government.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie1Plot
data.value: A thief, who steals corporate secrets through use of dream-sharing technology, is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a CEO."

data.name: MovieSection1Movie2Plot
data.value: With the help of a German bounty hunter, a freed slave sets out to rescue his wife from a brutal Mississippi plantation owner.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie3Plot
data.value: A frontiersman on a fur trading expedition in the 1820s fights for survival after being mauled by a bear and left for dead by members of his own hunting team.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie4Plot
data.value: An undercover cop and a mole in the police attempt to identify each other while infiltrating an Irish gang in South Boston.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie5Plot
data.value: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie6Plot
data.value: A short film promoting the opening of Melco-Crown's movie-themed resort and casino in Macau.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie7Plot
data.value: A writer and wall street trader, Nick, finds himself drawn to the past and lifestyle of his millionaire neighbor, Jay Gatsby.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie8Plot
data.value: In 1954, a U.S. marshal investigates the disappearance of a murderess who escaped from a hospital for the criminally insane.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie9Plot
data.value: A fisherman, a smuggler, and a syndicate of businessmen match wits over the possession of a priceless diamond.

data.name: MovieSection1Movie10Plot
data.value: The true story of Frank Abagnale Jr. who, before his 19th birthday, successfully conned millions of dollars' worth of checks as a Pan Am pilot, doctor, and legal prosecutor.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie1Plot
data.value: The true story of how the Boston Globe uncovered the massive scandal of child molestation and cover-up within the local Catholic Archdiocese, shaking the entire Catholic Church to its core.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie2Plot
data.value: Illustrated upon the progress of his latest Broadway play, a former popular actor's struggle to cope with his current life as a wasted actor is shown.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie3Plot
data.value: In the antebellum United States, Solomon Northup, a free black man from upstate New York, is abducted and sold into slavery.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie4Plot
data.value: Acting under the cover of a Hollywood producer scouting a location for a science fiction film, a CIA agent launches a dangerous operation to rescue six Americans in Tehran during the U.S. hostage crisis in Iran in 1980.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie5Plot
data.value: A silent movie star meets a young dancer, but the arrival of talking pictures sends their careers in opposite directions.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie6Plot
data.value: The story of King George VI of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland, his impromptu ascension to the throne and the speech therapist who helped the unsure monarch become worthy of it.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie7Plot
data.value: During the Iraq War, a Sergeant recently assigned to an army bomb squad is put at odds with his squad mates due to his maverick way of handling his work.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie7Cast
data.value: Jeremy Renner,Anthony Mackie,Brian Geraghty,Guy Pearce,Sergeant Matt Thompson,Ralph Fiennes

data.name: MovieSection2Movie8Plot
data.value: A Mumbai teen reflects on his upbringing in the slums when he is accused of cheating on the Indian Version of "Who Wants to be a Millionaire?"

data.name: MovieSection2Movie9Plot
data.value: Violence and mayhem ensue after a hunter stumbles upon a drug deal gone wrong and more than two million dollars in cash near the Rio Grande.

data.name: MovieSection2Movie10Plot
data.value: An undercover cop and a mole in the police attempt to identify each other while infiltrating an Irish gang in South Boston.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie1Plot
data.value: A blade runner must pursue and try to terminate four replicants who stole a ship in space and have returned to Earth to find their creator.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie2Plot
data.value: Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent 30 years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the maverick scientist Doc Brown.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie3Title
data.value: Back to the Future Part II

data.name: MovieSection3Movie3Plot
data.value: After visiting 2015, Marty McFly must repeat his visit to 1955 to prevent disastrous changes to 1985...without interfering with his first trip.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie4Title
data.value: Back to the Future Part III

data.name: MovieSection3Movie4Plot
data.value: Enjoying a peaceable existence in 1885, Doctor Emmet Brown is about to be killed by Buford "Mad Dog" Tannen. Marty McFly travels back in time to save his friend.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie5Plot
data.value: A human-looking indestructible cyborg is sent from 2029 to 1984 to assassinate a waitress, whose unborn son will lead humanity in a war against the machines, while a soldier from that war is sent to protect her at all costs.

data.name: MovieSection3Movie6Plot
data.value: A cyborg, identical to the one who failed to kill Sarah Connor, must now protect her ten year old son, John Connor, from a more advanced cyborg.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie1Plot
data.value: A woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler in postapocalyptic Australia in search for her home-land with the help of a group of female prisoners, a psychotic worshipper, and a drifter named Max.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie2Plot
data.value: An astronaut becomes stranded on Mars after his team assume him dead, and must rely on his ingenuity to find a way to signal to Earth that he is alive.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie3Plot
data.value: With the help of a mysterious pill that enables the user to access 100 percent of his brain abilities, a struggling writer becomes a financial wizard, but it also puts him in a new world with lots of dangers.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie4Plot
data.value: The son of a virtual world designer goes looking for his father and ends up inside the digital world that his father designed. He meets his father's corrupted creation and a unique ally who was born inside the digital world.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie5Plot
data.value: A medical engineer and an astronaut work together to survive after an accident leaves them adrift in space.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie6Plot
data.value: A veteran assigned to extract Earth's remaining resources begins to question what he knows about his mission and himself.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie7Plot
data.value: A cyborg policewoman attempts to bring down a nefarious computer hacker.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie8Plot
data.value: In the year 2154, the very wealthy live on a man-made space station while the rest of the population resides on a ruined Earth. A man takes on a mission that could bring equality to the polarized worlds.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie9Plot
data.value: When John Connor, leader of the human resistance, sends Sgt. Kyle Reese back to 1984 to protect Sarah Connor and safeguard the future, an unexpected turn of events creates a fractured timeline.

data.name: MovieSection4Movie10Plot
data.value: In 2074, when the mob wants to get rid of someone, the target is sent into the past, where a hired gun awaits - someone like Joe - who one day learns the mob wants to 'close the loop' by sending back Joe's future self for assassination.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie1Plot
data.value: A look at Wolverine's early life, in particular his time with the government squad Team X and the impact it will have on his later years.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie2Plot
data.value: After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie3Plot
data.value: With the world now aware of his identity as Iron Man, Tony Stark must contend with both his declining health and a vengeful mad man with ties to his father's legacy.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie4Plot
data.value: When Tony Stark's world is torn apart by a formidable terrorist called the Mandarin, he starts an odyssey of rebuilding and retribution.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie5Plot
data.value: Four young outsiders teleport to an alternate and dangerous universe which alters their physical form in shocking ways. The four must learn to harness their new abilities and work together to save Earth from a former friend turned enemy.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie6Plot
data.value: Bruce Banner, a genetics researcher with a tragic past, suffers an accident that causes him to transform into a raging green monster when he gets angry.

data.name: MovieSection5Movie7Plot
data.value: Bruce Banner, a scientist on the run from the U.S. Government, must find a cure for the monster he emerges whenever he loses his temper. However, Banner then must fight a soldier who unleashes himself as a threat stronger than he.
